   <conbody>
      <section class="- topic/section ">
         <sectiondiv class="- topic/sectiondiv ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">
               <note class="- topic/note ">The bypass mains needs to be available
and within tolerance. The static switch EN (BYP SSW) needs to be available.
The switch over do not interrupt the load.</note>
               <ol class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Switch to bypass operation:</p>
                     <ol id="Switch-to-bypass_1220236" class="- topic/ol ">
                        <li class="- topic/li ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Press the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Hash key</b> to enter the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">User stack</b>.</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="- topic/li ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Use the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Arrow keys</b> to navigate to <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Bypass operation</b>.</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="- topic/li ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Press the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Clock/number 1 key</b> to turn on bypass operation.</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="- topic/li ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Check that the green static switch EN (BYP SSW) LED on the
mimic diagram is illuminated.</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="- topic/li ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Press the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Back key</b> or wait 30 seconds to exit the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">User stack</b>.</p>
                        </li>
                     </ol>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Confirm any alarms by pressing the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">C key</b> twice.</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Make sure the system operates correctly and no alarms are present.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>The system is in bypass operation and load is supplied by the
bypass mains via the static switch EN (BYP SSW).</p>
         </sectiondiv>
